      <title>“绝地求生”开发商计划大举投资以求推出更多热门游戏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/-pubg-developer-plans-a-spending-spree-in-search-of-more-hits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[热门游戏《绝地求生：战场》的开发商 Krafton Inc. 今年计划斥资超过 2000 亿韩元（1.36 亿美元），投资十多家有前景的游戏工作室，彰显其成为全球出版业强国的雄心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/-pubg-developer-plans-a-spending-spree-in-search-of-more-hits</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 08:07:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Northvolt 将回收合资公司剩余股权出售给 Norsk Hydro</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/northvolt-sells-remaining-stake-in-recycling-jv-to-norsk-hydro</link>
      <description><![CDATA[破产的电池制造商 Northvolt AB 同意将其在回收合资企业中的剩余股份出售给 Norsk Hydro ASA，以便根据美国破产法第 11 章程序继续精简业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/northvolt-sells-remaining-stake-in-recycling-jv-to-norsk-hydro</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 07:35:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度杂货商面临快速配送应用带来的风险，DMart 遭遇冲击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/dmart-slips-on-profit-miss-as-discounts-rapid-deliveries-hurt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[人们担心的超快速配送平台对印度实体杂货店的冲击已经成为现实，印度最大的折扣超市连锁店之一的收益连续第九个季度令人失望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/dmart-slips-on-profit-miss-as-discounts-rapid-deliveries-hurt</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 05:54:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人工智能表现不佳导致 iPhone 假日季销量下降 5%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/iphone-sales-fall-in-2024-after-limited-apple-intelligence-rollout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年最后一个季度，苹果公司全球 iPhone 销量下滑 5%，并输给了中国竞争对手，这反映出 Apple Intelligence 在其美国以外最大的市场上的缺失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/iphone-sales-fall-in-2024-after-limited-apple-intelligence-rollout</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国将探索核能作为新人工智能数据中心计划的能源</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/uk-will-explore-nuclear-power-for-new-ai-data-center-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国正在规划建设数据中心的特殊区域，并将研究在这些区域使用核能，这是工党政府促进技术发展和人工智能生态系统的项目的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/uk-will-explore-nuclear-power-for-new-ai-data-center-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 22:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>ASML 支持的荷兰大学因网络攻击而停课</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/asml-backed-dutch-university-suspends-classes-after-cyber-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[荷兰顶尖理工大学是芯片机器制造商 ASML Holding NV 的主要人才输送中心，但在遭遇网络攻击后，该大学关闭了其计算机网络。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/asml-backed-dutch-university-suspends-classes-after-cyber-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 15:31:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果 2025 年计划：iPhone 大升级、智能家居推进和 AI 追赶</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2025-01-12/apple-2025-plans-iphone-17-smart-home-hub-ios-19-ai-apple-watch-ipads-m5</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果计划在 2025 年大展宏图，包括彻底改版 iPhone 产品线、推出新的 AI 功能、推出智能家居，以及更新很久没有更新的产品。此外：公司最新的首席财务官上任；迈阿密和中国的新店即将开业；戴尔在重大 PC 品牌重塑中厚颜无耻地抄袭了苹果的策略。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2025-01-12/apple-2025-plans-iphone-17-smart-home-hub-ios-19-ai-apple-watch-ipads-m5</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 13:00:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>DMart 母公司任命联合利华的 Asawa 于 2026 年接任首席执行官</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/dmart-parent-taps-unilever-s-asawa-to-take-over-as-ceo-in-2026</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在电子商务公司扩大快速配送业务的竞争中，印度零售连锁店 DMart 的运营商 Avenue Supermarts Ltd. 公布的利润低于预期，因此任命 Anshul Asawa 为其候任首席执行官。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/dmart-parent-taps-unilever-s-asawa-to-take-over-as-ceo-in-2026</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 06:51:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国股市在高标准财报季面临现实考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/the-stock-market-faces-reality-check-in-high-bar-earning-season</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着各家公司开始公布季度业绩，美国股市经历了两年来最强劲的反弹，现在正面临下一个重大考验，这将对估值是否超出基本现实提供重要的判断。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/the-stock-market-faces-reality-check-in-high-bar-earning-season</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 11 Jan 2025 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度 Infosys 和 HCL 准备应对特朗普总统任期内的商业前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/india-s-infosys-hcl-set-to-address-business-outlook-under-trump-presidency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度 IT 外包巨头 Infosys Ltd.、HCL Technologies Ltd. 和 Wipro Ltd. 的股价因唐纳德·特朗普赢得美国大选而上涨。他们将有机会在公布业绩时评论特朗普当选总统将如何影响其业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/india-s-infosys-hcl-set-to-address-business-outlook-under-trump-presidency</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 01:55:47 GMT</pubDate>
